82
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:25,470
Wait, Kamui!

83
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:28,640
Kamui!

84
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,330
Well, I'll be damned.

85
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:36,520
The sun has risen above Yoshiwara.

86
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:41,100
If that's risen up there, then the King of the Night has sunk below?

87
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,090
Who knows.

88
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,920
I have no interest in someone who's lost,

89
00:07:46,330 --> 00:07:47,450
...Abuto.

90
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:50,140
Aren't you so critical.

91
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,060
I worked my butt off, you know?

92
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:56,140
