126
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:01,300
There were still people in this universe

127
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:06,310
who possessed a totally different form of strength.

128
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:11,330
The samurai, with a sense of carnage that can rival the Yato.

129
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,170
