181
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:16,180
He's saying that he was the one who killed Hosen.

182
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:21,650
That Hosen's death was a result of the investigation into Yoshiwara.

183
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:25,650
Harusame shunned Hosen's excessive power.

184
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:30,710
The credit for the disposal of Hosen gives him total control over Yoshiwara.

185
00:13:31,850 --> 00:13:36,010
But he didn't do anything to Yoshiwara.

186
00:13:36,530 --> 00:13:39,430
Not only that, he didn't send any people either.

187
00:13:39,430 --> 00:13:41,020
He's leaving it completely alone.

188
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:43,600
That's right.

189
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,120
He has no interest in Yoshiwara.

190
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,970
His interest...

191
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,150
is in you.

192
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:55,450
He obtained Yoshiwara so other people wouldn't lay a hand on you all.

193
00:13:56,070 --> 00:13:58,640
In the end, Yoshiwara was saved, but...

194
00:13:59,650 --> 00:14:02,500
