216
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,220
See ya.

217
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,240
Don't die.

218
00:15:38,770 --> 00:15:40,470
Isn't that great?

219
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:42,020
