256
00:17:35,850 --> 00:17:36,960
Come on!

257
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,520
Hurry it up, you pig!

258
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,520
Woof!

259
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:41,380
